# Supabase in this repo

Use the SSR split — do not add a monolithic `lib/supabase.ts`.

```typescript
// Client Components / browser
import { createClient } from "@/lib/supabase/client";

// Server Components, Route Handlers, Server Actions
import { createClient } from "@/lib/supabase/server";
```

- Env vars: `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` (or `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY`)
- Auth: Supabase Auth; profile row stores division (B/C)
- MCP: `.cursor/mcp.json` — setup: `docs/supabase-mcp-cursor.md`
